, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Bd and Jel in xxvii. 90.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)  A thing"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that does not grow,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "increase;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "incapable of growth,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "increase; inanimate;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] as stone, in contradistinction to a tree [and an animal]. (Kull.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jamaAdN", "text_ar": "جَمَادٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "laka jaAmidu h`*aA AlmaAli", "text_ar": "لَكَ جَامِدُ هٰذَا المَالِ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "wa*aAy^ibuhu", "text_ar": "وَذَايِبُهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, L, K *) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "To thee belongs,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shall belong, what consists of gold and silver"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "or the like inanimate things"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "],"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "of this property, and what consists of live stock, thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L, K:) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what consists of stones, thereof, and what consists of trees, thereof:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "what is solid, thereof, and what is fluid,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "liquid, thereof."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(L.) ―         -b4-  [Hence its application in lexicology and grammar to (assumed tropical:)  A noun"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "that is not an inf. n. nor derived from an inf. n.;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a noun"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "having the quality of a real substantive"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aisomi EayonK", "text_ar": "اِسْمِ عَيْنٍ"},